occasional /əˈkeɪʒənəl/

1. ADJ Occasional means happening sometimes, but not regularly or often. 偶尔的 

例： I've had occasional mild headaches all my life. 我此生一直有偶尔的轻微头疼。 

2. occasionally ADV 偶尔地 

例： He still misbehaves occasionally. 他仍偶尔行为不乖。

